 we conclude that a larger sample of\nsimilarly well-observed novae is needed to understand the origin and variation\nof gamma rays in novae.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2017 18:50:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Nov 2017 16:26:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-31"}
