ying the effects of turbulent energy dissipation on group-wide scales\nthat may provide clues about the heating and cooling of gas at high-z in early\ngalaxy and protogalaxy formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jan 2017 04:18:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2017 20:05:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-15"}
