h power factor) by 29% compared to a\nconventional customer. Similar insights are also observed for a case with three\ncustomers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jan 2017 13:46:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-13"}
